==English==

===Etymology===
From [[dish]] + [[wash]] + [[-er]]

===Noun===
'''dishwasher'''  (''plural:'' '''[[dishwashers]]''')

## A [[machine]] for washing dishes. Someone who washes dishes, especially one [[hired]] to wash dishes in a [[restaurant]].


